description:
Discover the ultimate blend of capability, comfort, and style with this exceptional 2025 Ford F-150 STX. Boasting a powerful 2.7L V6 EcoBoost engine, 4-wheel drive, and a rugged off-road-tuned suspension, this truck is ready to tackle any adventure with confidence.

Equipped with the FX4 Off-Road Package, featuring off-road tuned front shock absorbers, skid plates, and 18-inch black painted aluminum wheels with all-terrain tires for enhanced traction and capability.
Enjoy the convenience of the Mobile Office Package, which includes a console worksurface and 400W cab and bed outlets, transforming your truck into a mobile workspace.
Standout features include LED fog lamps, a dual-tip exhaust, and a retractable rear center step for easy access.
The Rapid Red Metallic Tinted Clearcoat exterior exudes a bold and confident presence, complemented by the sleek black accents and running boards.

This F-150 STX is more than just a capable workhorse; it's a versatile companion that seamlessly blends rugged performance with modern amenities. Experience the perfect balance of power, utility, and style with this exceptional 2025 Ford F-150 STX.

With its impressive fuel efficiency, delivering up to 24 mpg on the highway, this F-150 STX not only excels in capability but also in cost-effectiveness. Whether you're tackling tough job sites, navigating off-road terrain, or simply commuting in style, this truck is ready to take on any challenge.

Step inside and discover the thoughtfully designed interior, featuring a SYNC 4 infotainment system, power windows, and a rear window defroster for your comfort and convenience. The tray-style floor liner and carpet mats provide added protection, while the split-folding rear seat offers versatile cargo-hauling options.

Safety is paramount, and this F-150 STX delivers with features like dual front impact airbags, electronic stability control, and a rearview camera with rear parking sensors for added peace of mind.

Experience the ultimate in capability, comfort, and style with this exceptional 2025 Ford F-150 STX. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable truck can enhance your driving experience and exceed your expectations.
